window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Alex and Enea are back in the Crystal Sphere, where, in their absence, a catastrophe has struck. Virtual reality is now controlled by the Reapers: hybrid identities evolved from high-level NPCs who kill human players to harvest their neurograms.</p> <p>Reapers are constantly on the prowl for more neurograms. No one is safe from their cannibalistic greed.</p> <p>Survival in this new world becomes an ever-increasing challenge. A Reaper army is about to invade the Agrion cluster. Rion Castle has become the players' last outpost - but the struggle is too unequal.</p>"; 
